OL,6,GFollowing technical configurations to
OL,7,GSaorview's second multiplex last
OL,8,Gmonth, further changes have been
OL,9,Grolled out this week, increasing
OL,10,Gavailable capacity on Ireland's
OL,11,Gdigital terrestrial TV platform.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, services on Saorview
OL,14,Fmultiplex one were compressed,
OL,15,Fcreating capacity to relaunch the 2rn
OL,16,Ftest card on channel 51. This in turn
OL,17,Fis part of a test of HbbTV on the
OL,18,Fplatform.
OL,3,CFurther technical upgrades as
OL,4,CSaorview plans for the future
