OL,6,FAccording to 2rn, these test
OL,7,Ftransmissions are broadcast to the
OL,8,FNorDig standard ` HbbTV 1.5
OL,9,Fspecification.
OL,11,FThe primary function of these tests
OL,12,Fare to ensure that the Saorview
OL,13,Fplatform is ready to accommodate
OL,14,Ffuture development in this area and
OL,15,Fto ensure that Irish broadcasters
OL,16,Fwishing to take advantage of newer
OL,17,Ftechnologies (in order to bring Irish
OL,18,Fviewers an improved and richer
OL,19,Finteractive experience) are
OL,20,Faccommodated.
OL,3,CFurther technical upgrades as
OL,4,CSaorview plans for the future
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
