OL,6,FBut there's a wider reason behind the
OL,7,FHbbTV tests. Currently Saorview only
OL,8,Fsupports MHEG5 for text and
OL,9,Finteractive services. MHEG5 is being
OL,10,Fphased out, not just by platforms,
OL,11,Fbut also by device manufacturers.
OL,13,FAnd broadcasters are reviewing the
OL,14,Fpotential for HbbTV to deliver future
OL,15,Fteletext and interactive options,
OL,16,Fsuch as a red button link to the
OL,17,Fbroadcaster's streaming service as
OL,18,Fused by the BBC to connect the red
OL,19,Fbutton to iPlayer.
OL,3,CFurther technical upgrades as
OL,4,CSaorview plans for the future
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
