OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F341A1686136862
OL,6,FA look at the specs of a recent
OL,7,FSamsung Smart TV confirms Samsung is
OL,8,Fonly keeping MHEG5 support for users
OL,9,Fin Ireland. In other countries, MHEG5
OL,10,Fsupport is typically disabled by
OL,11,Fdefault. HbbTV (up to version 2.0.3)
OL,12,Fis supported instead.
OL,14,FIn the UK, this means a newer Samsung
OL,15,FTV may load the BBC HbbTV connected
OL,16,Fred button app that links to iPlayer
OL,17,Finstead of the old text-based MHEG5
OL,18,Fservice.
OL,3,CFurther technical upgrades as
OL,4,CSaorview plans for the future
