OL,6,FSaorview hasn't yet indicated what
OL,7,Fmay happen with the extra capacity
OL,8,Fand what types of extra interactive
OL,9,Ffunctionality may become available.
OL,10,FHowever, the latest developments put
OL,11,FSaorview in a good position to stay
OL,12,Frelevant, and a viable complement to
OL,13,Fthe plethora of apps available on
OL,14,Fsmart TVs.
